summary: Giant buns located a little bit outside Whiterun. Don\'t eat them all right away because that\'s all that there is.
descriptionHtml:
What? I need a reason for this now? Just some giant buns located a little bit outside Whiterun.

Giant Bun Pros: They gib you 200 instant health.

Giant Bun Cons: They weight 100 lbs.

Don\'t eat them all right away because what you see on the ground is all that there is.

Perfect waybread for the Dragonderp.
author: brokendeck
